analysis: The agent incorrectly capitalized the values for "investmentSize" and "marketDynamics" ("Moderate", "Dynamic") instead of using the expected lowercase ("moderate", "dynamic"), causing a mismatch with the expected function call parameters.

The agent called the correct function with almost the right parameters but specified "outputDetail": "Detailed" instead of the required "outputDetail": "Summary" as expected, resulting in a parameter mismatch.
The agent used an invalid value "Comprehensive" for the "detailLevel" parameter instead of the required "Detailed," resulting in a parameter mismatch and failure to match the expected function call.

The agent added an unsupported parameter "weatherDetail" to the FlightStatus_checkFlightAndWeather function call; the tool only accepts "airportCode" and "flightNumber" as parameters. This caused the evaluator to reject the function call as non-matching.
The agent failed to include the required "ratingThreshold": "good" parameter in the function call, resulting in an incomplete and non-matching invocation for recommending highly rated Sci-Fi games.
The agent incorrectly formatted the "rating" parameter as "4.5" instead of using the expected categorical value "high", resulting in a function call that didn't match the required schema.
